Package org.vast.json

Class JsonStreamReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.json.JsonStreamReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamConstants, javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamReader, JsonConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GMLJsonStreamReader, SWEJsonStreamReader
    public class JsonStreamReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamReader, JsonConstants

    Stream reader implementation for unmarshalling SWE metadata from JSON.
    This transforms JSON parsing events into XML parsing events so it can be used with existing StAX parsers.

    Since:
    Jan 26, 2017
